title: [RG.REBOOT] Dubstep Sampler Vol.1 (2013) {MP3-320CBR}
description:
Music Notes 
~~~~~~~~~~~
Compiled from WEB sources. Personally arranged by REBOOT.OP.

Songs are all dubstep, a few are trappy, (like Urban Metaphor) but still dubstep.

If you want a Vol.2, please comment with the request. I put together songs that
most people have not heard or are new.
